    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/0544ae26078eb26cc66c8020d18c3199.poster.avif?t=1770262459\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/0544ae26078eb26cc66c8020d18c3199.webm?t=1770262459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/0544ae26078eb26cc66c8020d18c3199.mp4?t=1770262459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for checking out Fish Combat: Accelerated!!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish Combat is a Movement Base Fighting game built for speedrunning. Every system in the game, from combat to gravity defying platforming, encourages you to move FAST!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is still early in development and will use a similar movement system to our other title, Hyper Fin. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've played that and would like an Action-Adventure, Speedrunning game in a similar world, please give this a wish list and we'll move things along faster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/88ce537b3f18f6e85048988867bb2ea6.poster.avif?t=1770262459\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/88ce537b3f18f6e85048988867bb2ea6.webm?t=1770262459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144020/extras/88ce537b3f18f6e85048988867bb2ea6.mp4?t=1770262459\" ty